snippet.title: mgrace10
snippet.description:
"It is not the teacher before you that manifests what you perceive as an AWAKENING,, but the AWAKENING within you that manifests what you perceive as a teacher" 

I am a student and a teacher in this game called Life, with so many facets resonating within,. An Artist at the core like we all are, creating from a blank canvas, That is Life. . 
This shift is making us change and choose tracks "Let's commit to begin an unstoppable force of inner peace in this world"
